summary: This mod aims to create a drug culture influenced by the lore of the Elder Scrolls along side a story I made a while ago, to fit my character.
descriptionHtml: This mod adds a few races, a new island (Gagonia, a play off of Argonia), the Magic Mushrooms (from Dogola), and a few other things. As the mod progresses I plan to add more to the world space, more cells, more NPCs and a few simple quests.
author: Gagi420
